headline: KeyCorp’s (NYSE:KEY) Q4 CY2025: Beats On Revenue
summary: Regional banking company KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) reported Q4 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 12.5% year on year to $2.01 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.41 per share was 6.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
